[Jingyeong gruñe]

00:35:53.423 --> 00:35:55.008
[♪ aguijón dramático]

00:35:56.509 --> 00:35:57.510
¿Hola?

00:36:00.138 --> 00:36:01.139
Este es mi coche, doctor.

00:36:04.184 --> 00:36:05.435
Doctor.

00:36:05.894 --> 00:36:06.895
Ey.

